                <note>4.1 Smith … mate. 4.3] <hi rend="italic">crossed pencil</hi></note>
                <note>5.1 You … species; 5.3] <hi rend="italic">double scored blue crayon</hi></note>
                <note>6.1 I have … butterflies. 6.3] <hi rend="italic">scored blue crayon</hi></note>
                <note>7.4 as the … female. 7.5] <hi rend="italic">double scored blue crayon, pencil</hi>; ‘Looks to like correlation— important if mature sexes differ.’ <hi rend="italic">added pencil</hi></note>
                <note>8.2 the females … experience, 8.3] <hi rend="italic">triple scored blue crayon</hi></note>
